    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The morning starts with a coffee and game of Sudoku on in the sun on the beach. Austin arrives with a bag of local tobacco that is truly quite hectic stuff - it’s definitely going to be an aid to stop smoking when the sabbatical is done. Breakfast arrives, we start packing up and take a dip in the water before hitting the road.",
            "link": null
          },
