    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It’s about 50m down the road and the checkin is easy. We get the last room - a four person dorm that we luckily have to ourselves. We drop bags and dive into the perfectly warm lake lapping the shore. After that we retreat a couple meters to some deck chairs where a beer, book and writing causes time to melt away. We book a snorkelling tour for tomorrow to Thumbi island.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "It’s about 50m down the road and the checkin is easy. We get the last room - a four person dorm that we luckily have to ourselves. We drop bags and dive into the perfectly warm lake lapping the shore. After that we retreat a couple meters to some deck chairs where a beer, book and writing causes time to melt away. We book a snorkelling tour for tomorrow to Thumbi island.",
